---
title: Kumara & Basil Pesto Risotto with Pine Nut Pangrattato & Herbs
description: This rich, creamy risotto comes together in the oven, leaving you free to create a quick and crunchy pine nut pangrattato to sprinkle
over at the end. Such a small factor takes this plant-based veggie meal to the next level – taste it and see!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pumpkin-basil-pesto-risotto-2d575fbf.jpg
